HW 2

Take the Random File Series and do the following:

1.)  Open the windows in the center of the screen.

2.)  Add HotKeys to the buttons in the window.

3.)  Make sure YOU control the cursor's focus !!!!

4.) Enable the enter key to move thropugh the textfields as well as the buttons.

5.) Update the Window Adapter !!!!

***5.) Finally, write a separate program called UpdateRandomFile with full functionality (see above)  
that will allow the user to update the random file.

***6.) You can also create a program called DeleteRandomFile that will delete one or more records !!!